lead_paragraph: A stray bullet cut through the plastic roof of the equestrian media center on Saturday, alarming journalists and underlining concerns about the host city's ability to guarantee security at the world's biggest sporting event.

headline.print_headline: Stray Bullet Flies Into Equestrian Media Center
